          "subtitle": "Core principles for responsible AI use",
          "slidecontent": "• AI does not reduce your compliance obligations, it adds new ones\n• Always know where patient data goes when it enters an AI tool\n• Audit trails matter\n• Consent, transparency, and data minimisation remain non-negotiable under GDPR and HIPAA\n• Your organisation is accountable for AI outputs, even when the vendor is at fault\n• As a next step, review your current AI tools against your data processing agreements and flag any gaps to your compliance team"
